*   **draft-ietf-spice-oidc-cwt:** Co-chair Christopher Inacio to transition the document status in the Data Tracker to initiate the AD write-up.
*   **Architecture Draft:** Brent Sundell to resubmit the architecture document under an individual draft name (e.g., `draft-zundel-spice-architecture`) so the WG can formally initiate an adoption call on the mailing list.

